[[File:Zombie.jpg|thumb|right|200px|An undead Sith]]
'''Sith undead''' were long-dead [[Sith/Legends|Sith]] warriors that lay in the catacombs of the [[Dark Force Temple]] on [[Dromund Kaas/Legends|Dromund Kaas]]. Ghastly in appearance, their weapon of choice was [[Force lightning/Legends|Force lightning]].

On alien presence, their rotten bodies were reanimated by the [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side]] aura of the Temple to protect it. [[Mara Jade Skywalker|Mara Jade]] [[Mission to Dromund Kaas (New Republic)|faced]] these warriors during her quest for [[Kyle Katarn]] on Dromund Kaas.

==Behind the scenes==
Sith undead are not mentioned in the game's manual. This is most likely to make their appearance a surprise.

